{"tid":1996283,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"電力裝置係偉大發明","createTime":"2020-05-01T00:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T09:43:21.000Z","uid":231600,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"eb6d61ba0adb9e2e1127cfda6aacf1ff8f904d3a","tid":1996283,"uid":231600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T00:47:52.000Z","msg":"風力 水力都係好創新，但點都好，電力可以話係當時一個跨世代發明。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">電力</span>&mdash;-喺我哋呢個時代，任何野都一定靠電力維持。例如電視機，電話，電腦。呢啲日常用品係基本野，冇咗電，我哋連開都開唔到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你話有風力發電，但風力發電只不過係一個額外供電方式，風並不是為電而生。<br />\n<br />\n所以電係凌駕於一切，水同風永遠都不及電。"},{"pid":"0d453df0a3dcbb6e4acb9521e1cf527bd181c6d1","tid":1996283,"uid":43575,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T00:53:27.000Z","msg":"古代唔洗電力都起到石金字塔，遠遠超越現代科技水平"},{"pid":"253de78011d12a2a23341f187957d78662ed130f","tid":1996283,"uid":231600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0d453df0a3dcbb6e4acb9521e1cf527bd181c6d1","tid":1996283,"uid":43575,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T00:53:27.000Z","msg":"古代唔洗電力都起到石金字塔，遠遠超越現代科技水平"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T00:55:00.000Z","msg":"但古代文明已經大部份消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經冇乜可能重現倒嗰時嘅文明力"},{"pid":"e7942bba307e5ddcdd791910137ca41dfd109341","tid":1996283,"uid":174601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T00:55:30.000Z","msg":"有電力少左好多奴隸"},{"pid":"8cb6bf1e7425993bfc0a15cae4d8d0aaa7d0f7a1","tid":1996283,"uid":231600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7942bba307e5ddcdd791910137ca41dfd109341","tid":1996283,"uid":174601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T00:55:30.000Z","msg":"有電力少左好多奴隸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T00:58:23.000Z","msg":"電力係因為要依靠佢嘅嘢多咗，所以先比其他野重要"},{"pid":"35dda47f799c1c56aa6a32f3d38f462fb6b208f9","tid":1996283,"uid":270237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T00:59:18.000Z","msg":